We used ConceptNet for training and testing\footnote{Observe that in the previous unsupervised setting, the other datasets were needed because the source sentences underlying ConceptNet are unnatural. Its structured statements themselves are of good quality.} and report precision and recall@k. The training and testing sets contain 
186k and 23k triples.